<p>In a way, Alex Turner became a living barometer for the political climate. Through every election and every shift in the balance of power, Alex’s unique attributes offered him a profound connection to the heartbeats of American democracy. Some say his exterior changes spurred on a deeper internal metamorphosis—one that transformed a bewildered teenager into a passionate, engaged citizen committed to understanding and shaping the world around him.</p></div>

